public abstract class CCTermConnEv
extends CCCallEv
implements javax.telephony.callcontrol.events.CallCtlTermConnEv

This is a parent class for all CallControl TerminalConnection events.

These are parallel events to those generated for the base TerminalConnection. These are sent to Observers that implement the CallControlCallObserver interface. Creation date: (2000-08-03 11:45:53)
